name: Boi Vaquim
description: The legend of Boi Vaquim emerged among the cowboys who inhabited the southern region of the country. The mythical bull, with golden quotes and bird's wings, released sparks from its horns and frightened the inhabitants of the region. This character caused a mixture of fascination and fear in the residents of Rio Grande do Sul: some cowboys fear encountering the beast during their rides, while others, in search of fame, dream of lassoing and dominating the Boi Vaquim.<Crypto Legends | A Series by Renancio Monte | 2021>
